 \emph{(Guide: Prof. Bimal Roy
, Aug'19 - Feb'20)} \\[-0.6cm]
\begin{itemize}\itemsep \isep
\item  Wrote an R code for implementation of the existing model and comparisons with other models, proposed 2 tweaks to the existent model to improved accuracy and lesser computational complexity.
\end{itemize}

